      <span class="eyebrow">Commercial</span>
      <h1>
        Commercial electrical work for owners and managers who need cleaner
        execution in active spaces
      </h1>
      <p>
        Commercial projects usually have two pressures at once: the electrical
        problem needs to be solved correctly, and the property still needs to
        function while the work is happening. Top Tier Electrical supports light
        commercial spaces with practical troubleshooting, lighting upgrades,
        service changes, and tenant-ready planning that reduce confusion and
        keep the scope understandable.
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>
          Useful for offices, retail, mixed-use properties, shops, and light
          industrial spaces
        </li>
        <li>
          Strong fit for occupied buildings where cleanliness and communication
          matter
        </li>
        <li>
          Clearer planning for owners, facility leads, and general contractors
        </li>
      </ul>
